# Keep debug symbolication maps out of the deploy. Flutter's web build emits
# ~8 MB of *.symbols files (CanvasKit/skwasm stack-trace maps); the runtime
# never fetches them, so they only bloat the upload. Everything users actually
# download (main.dart.js, the selected canvaskit.wasm, tree-shaken fonts) is
# served brotli-compressed by Vercel and stays.
*.symbols
